Customer:
1. Login/logout
2.View tickets (his/her tickets of any group)
3. Create new ticket - id, summary, details, created date/time, status, group, priority(1-5), assignee, requestor, problem category



Service Agent:
1. Login/logout
2. View tickets (of assigned group)
3. Update status of ticket



Admin:

1. Login/logout
2. Create customers/service agents - id, username, password, email, contact no, group (only for agent),
3. View tickets (all tickets)
4. Create groups  - id, name
5. Add categories